      "description": "Box-bubble topology for the two-loop four-gluon amplitude in $N=2$ SQCD. One-loop box with a self-energy (bubble) insertion on one internal propagator. Diagrams (i) and (j) have adjoint gluon-loop and fundamental quark-loop bubble insertions respectively. Propagator denominators defined in Ref. [Johansson:2017bfl]. At the conformal point $N_f=2N_c$, diagrams (i) and (j) manifestly cancel from the integrand. Diagram (i) contributes only to $N=4$ SYM part; (j) contributes only to $S$ (the non-conformal part).",
